result.name: 極之好粥麵茶餐廳

reviews.text: Great service and tasty food. Great soup
Clay pot rice is excellent, service is good too.
Delicious stir-fry dishes, popular hot old fashioned clay pot rice with various choices of meat and vegetables. Stir fry dishes are on the expensive side as in small portions.

We chanced upon this accidentally when we realised the Kam Wah CCT is closed only when we reach there. But I think we hit a Jem here. 

We had a firm but yet playfully friendly male waiter(suspecting to be the male boss?) that got our order, though I spoke to him in Cantonese he was still patient as he realised that we are tourists. Even offered to help bring a few chairs for us to place our over sized bags from our looting adventure.

There is so many types to choose from their speciality claypot rice and yes I finally find one stall that has the burn rice on the pot. The flavour of the waxed meat rice was just right, not too overbearing. The smooth chicken rice has the oil from the fresh chicken embracing the rice as it heats up the meat and the radish with beef cartilage is so sweet yet soft but not too salty. The male server even helped us to get the burn rice part out of the claypot... it was so good and brings back lots of childhood memories of food we use to have back then.
delicious claypot rice, seating is tiny and probably gonna share table... also u need to wait at least 30 mins for the rice after ordering ...

result.formatted_address: 香港旺角通菜街154號號地下
result.name: 極之好粥麵茶餐廳

reviews.text:
實在垃圾, 食個早餐, 碗沙嗲牛麵啲湯超鹹, 餐飽又不給牛油
另外, 個男伙計用埋啲港式普通話去招呼兩個大陸女遊客, 遊客不知點什麼, 就問有什麼招牌, 個伙計一味叫個遊客點炒豬腸粉, 話好好味, 冇介紹錯... 來回過招了數次, 女遊客終於落搭, 原來碟炒豬腸粉索價 $58.00, 嘩！ 去大酒樓食都唔駛咁貴嗎？ 擺明是呃大陸客啦
唯獨是太子地區 $33.00 食個早餐算合理, 不過下次零願多給幾蚊去華星食個有水準的早餐
煲仔飯好好味，麵味道一般啦👍👍👍

炒蜆正，煲仔飯都正
但可惜既係永遠炒蜆起任何餐廳都食唔夠
[小提示，煲仔飯落豉油落起边]
Great service and tasty food. Great soup
Clay pot rice is excellent, service is good too.
